    "body": "Problem: win_linetabsize() includes wrap overhead from 'linebreak' based on current window width, but the result sizes the window, causing a feedback loop.\r\n\r\nSolution: Temporarily set w_view_width to Columns before measuring.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
